data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Well maintained home on a quiet NE Salem cul de sac. Total open floor plan downstairs with tasteful updates. Premium custom blinds. Four bedrooms upstairs with two full baths. Spacious primary bedroom has onsuite bath and walk in closet. Covered patio in a private secluded fenced back yard for pets. Low maintenance 12x24 above ground pool. Two storage sheds, one is insulated. RV storage and extra storage for recreational toys or boat. Close walk to schools.
